{"tid":1617270,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"喂喂喂 星期六 反蒙面大遊行 誠邀大家創意大爆炸 希望我個廁所板會上到外媒頭條","createTime":"2019-10-03T17:04:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T10:52:57.000Z","uid":229033,"like":101,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"7ccf2583628f078cfbe8d4ddc54a93aa060cc436","tid":1617270,"uid":229033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T17:04:04.000Z","msg":"星期六係全民蒙面遊行<br />\n雖然一個口罩一頂Cap帽而家真係基本<br />\n但隨著國際其他議題(e.g.韓國撐文在寅/反文運動)<br />\n為左確保香港人嘅議題依然受世界關注<br />\n我想提議用奇招去引發世界關注<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我希望大家可以運用自己嘅創意 <br />\n用一個特別嘅蒙面形式<br />\n等全世界都可以知道 香港人係好有諗頭好有創意<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我呢個idea係被日本嘅「日常cosplay」節啟發<br />\n以下我尊登搵左啲圖做參考比大家睇下<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e5MLD0w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe5MLD0w.png&h=5760c109&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wweQP7d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwweQP7d.png&h=ce224371&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/93B7Skz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F93B7Skz.png&h=fb9c5e49&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7jMS3sf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7jMS3sf.png&h=c16a8ce6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我知道可能有人會質疑咁算唔算快樂抗爭/嘉年華<br />\n但其實呢個提議係特意適用比和理非<br />\n希望你地可以用另類方法 將香港抗爭保溫<br />\n亦都符合你地嘅特點同原則 <br />\n希望勇武嘅手足可以理解我只想搵個方法比和理非係星期六發揮重要作用<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: navy;\">最後 我係度承諾大家 <br />\n若然呢個post可以過8000正皮加推爆開post2 <br />\n我會買個廁所板當日扮演廁所 同各位一齊行！<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">希望大家當日唔係hea而係睇完覺得可以<br />\n真係認真諗下放啲咩上塊面蒙面<br />\n話比全世界知香港要推反蒙面法<br />\n而反對嘅聲音升勢持續浩大<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n解散警隊 刻不容緩<br />\n港人同心 和勇不分</span></span>"},{"pid":"7324d024e2536554e32c0dd757d701b01ef66291","tid":1617270,"uid":145225,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T17:07:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y78qD0p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy78qD0p.png&h=2ea920e5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x9etBM5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx9etBM5.png&h=f74ca2cf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dbeb47b5eda31bcd85e72d38b8cf47939aa4ff99","tid":1617270,"uid":229033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T17:07:20.000Z","msg":"十連推"},{"pid":"bfeac40054707e8fc70c76ac71965bcd8e480250","tid":1617270,"uid":229033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T17:07:32.000Z","msg":"一"},{"pid":"378bc7ba32e243891a64f3d594ecb724904c640f","tid":1617270,"uid":229033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T17:07:44.000Z","msg":"二"},{"pid":"3f913f9e9f7baa5bbdee26b8ca02a8fc542fdc87","tid":1617270,"uid":229033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T17:08:01.000Z","msg":"三"},{"pid":"36ecd785c483ed38263eb45931dcf33b0f598e5c","tid":1617270,"uid":229033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T17:08:11.000Z","msg":"四"},{"pid":"6bf3449f476118396e5d3bcaea35faaec4b3a4b2","tid":1617270,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T17:08:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05491e7be41c95bdf2f2c8d6188b41819490b744","tid":1617270,"uid":229033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T17:08:34.000Z","msg":"五"},{"pid":"c29b1f71fef54531fd2f861c763e71d8c515f25e","tid":1617270,"uid":229033,"like":0,"dislike":